      <title>苹果计划将新款 iPhone 出货量提高 10%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-11/apple-aims-to-ship-10-more-new-iphones-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果计划在今年下半年出货至少 9000 万台 iPhone 16 设备，并希望在经历了艰难的 2023 年之后，人工智能服务能够刺激其新产品线的需求。彭博情报的 Anurag Rana 与 Caroline Hyde 和 Ed Ludlow 一起讨论“彭博科技”。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-11/apple-aims-to-ship-10-more-new-iphones-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 19:12:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杰富瑞因诉讼关闭对冲基金 352 Capital</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/jefferies-winds-down-hedge-fund-352-capital-in-wake-of-lawsuit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，杰富瑞金融集团 (Jefferies Financial Group Inc.) 正在减少旗下对冲基金 352 Capital 的交易头寸，此前该基金以其前投资组合经理涉嫌欺诈而对其进行起诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/jefferies-winds-down-hedge-fund-352-capital-in-wake-of-lawsuit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 18:56:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Citadel 计划提升交易市场份额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-11/citadel-s-plan-to-boost-trading-market-share-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 Ken Griffin 的 Citadel Securities 内部，一项处理更多华尔街交易的新战略正在初具规模 — — 这对全球陷入困境的银行和经纪公司产生了影响。目标是为这些公司提供白标交易服务。彭博社的 Katherine Doherty 和 Sonali Basak 对此进行了报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-11/citadel-s-plan-to-boost-trading-market-share-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 18:46:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Dollar General 同意就工作场所安全指控与美国达成和解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/dollar-general-dg-agrees-to-settle-with-us-over-store-safety-allegations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Dollar General Corp. 同意与美国安全监管机构达成一项全面的公司范围和解，这对于这家美国最普遍的零售商来说可能是一个转折点，因为多年来，该公司的门店安全状况一直饱受争议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/dollar-general-dg-agrees-to-settle-with-us-over-store-safety-allegations</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 18:32:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Rudin 联席首席执行官谈及对商业房地产的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-11/rudin-co-ceo-on-concerns-around-commercial-real-estate-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Rudin 联席首席执行官 Samantha Rudin Earls 讨论了商业房地产、将商业建筑改造成住宅公寓以及回馈纽约市的担忧。她在“彭博市场”节目中与 Scarlet Fu 和 Abigail Doolittle 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-11/rudin-co-ceo-on-concerns-around-commercial-real-estate-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 18:31:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
