      <title>美联储降息预期导致股市轮动，大型股遭遇重创：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街交易员押注美联储将能够很快降息，导致债券收益率暴跌 — — 同时推动了推动股市牛市的科技巨头的大规模轮换。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 22:35:05 GMT</pubDate>
